description:
Life is better on the trail, provided you have the right shirt. The fabric provides sun protection to shield you from harsh rays, and it's light and breathable to wear through the day's peak heat. When sun exposure is particularly intense, flip up the collar and snap it in place.Durable double-weave nylon blend has UPF 50+ sun protection.Hidden snap in collar clips up for additional coverage.Underarm gusset and dropped shoulder seam allow unrestricted movement.Forward shoulder seam is comfortable under backpack straps.Underarm eyelets vent excess heat.

